---
// "Why I started My LA Therapy" — founder photo now uses the real Brooke portrait
---
<section style="background:var(--mist);padding:72px 36px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:52px;align-items:center;" class="split pad-fluid">
  <div style="position:relative;">
    <div style="aspect-ratio:4/5;border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden;background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--clay-soft),var(--peach));">
      <img src="/images/founder-brooke.webp" alt="Brooke Sprowl, LCSW — Founder & Clinical Director of My LA Therapy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:36% center;" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--terracotta);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px;">From the founder</div>
    <h2 class="h2-fluid" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:38px;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 18px;color:var(--forest-ink);">Why I started My LA Therapy</h2>
    <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.62;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px;">I learned the hard way that insight alone won't change your life. I was self-aware — I'd done the work on paper — yet the patterns held. What finally moved me was a therapist skilled enough to intervene below the surface, where intellectual understanding becomes real, embodied change.</p>
    <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.62;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 24px;">So I built the practice I wished I'd found. Exceptional therapy requires exceptional humans — so I hand-pick every clinician for that rare blend of training, self-awareness, and presence, then match you with care and back it with a guarantee. Because finding the right fit should never be a gamble.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;">
      <img src="/images/brooke-headshot.webp" alt="Brooke Sprowl" style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;" />
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:19px;color:var(--forest-ink);font-style:italic;"><b>Brooke Sprowl, LCSW</b></div><div style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted-3);">Founder &amp; Clinical Director</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
